1

00:00:00,000  -->  00:00:02,400
The third measure of center,

2

00:00:02,400  -->  00:00:06,135
aims at providing us the most common value in the data set.

3

00:00:06,135  -->  00:00:07,720
In this data set,

4

00:00:07,720  -->  00:00:09,580
this is the value of three.

5

00:00:09,580  -->  00:00:14,185
The value that occurs most often is known as the Mode.

6

00:00:14,185  -->  00:00:16,940
These are all three potential measures of center.

7

00:00:16,940  -->  00:00:19,580
The Mean or the average,

8

00:00:19,580  -->  00:00:22,155
the Median or the middle value,

9

00:00:22,155  -->  00:00:25,820
and the Mode or the most frequent value.
